WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
Audio Cutter's start screen shows a drop zone for a local WAV or MP3 file.

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.000
A WAV file is selected, and its waveform appears for inspection.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Exact In and Out times are entered, moving the gold trim handles to select the range.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.000
WAV output remains selected, then Cut & download is chosen.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.500
Audio Cutter confirms that the finished file was downloaded locally without an upload.
